                .radio
                  label
                    input(type="radio", name="optradio" value="0")
                    | 12:00pm - 1:30pm
                .radio
                  label
                    input(type="radio", name="optradio" value="0")
                    | 1:30pm - 3:00pm
            .col-xs-12.col-sm-6
              span.lead Description:
              p.
                Deal with people and walk a ton. Involves
                lots of time working on your feet helping people get the
                food they came for
